{"tid":939743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警戒！網友預告東京車站隨機砍人　「來場殺人遊戲吧」","createTime":"2018-12-13T11:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T14:44:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":221,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"4c24906b1a998332920425654cdda09e76f5065c","tid":939743,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:14:30.000Z","msg":"日本有網友在《推特》上發文指出，將在13日、14日在東京車站殺人「來場大量殺人遊戲吧」，並稱至少會殺10人，引發熱議後，警方已經在東京車站警戒。<br />\n <br />\n據《BIGLOBE》報導，日本網友「りゅうた 人口削減計画 最後の仕事 (@r_t1379) 」12日晚上在《推特》發文說，「我的人生大概已經到了終點，但是我不會後悔，我明天、後天會在東京車站進行隨機殺人，殺10人後我也會死，我的目的是對社會跟女性復仇，大家就在血海中尖叫吧」。<br />\n <br />\n該帳號目前已被凍結，該篇文章在網路上引起熱議後，警視廳已在JR東京車站附近強化警戒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99D7T02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99D7T02.png&h=c65d8005&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TeJ4bNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTeJ4bNJ.png&h=3ca024ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2e7d3aafb9b30c713167f55ab30b459dfd82af8","tid":939743,"uid":84102,"like":30,"dislike":433,"score":-403,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:15:15.000Z","msg":"Skr🤙🏻"},{"pid":"984edfdee21f7d0c791f18d968f6cfdece10b6f5","tid":939743,"uid":45120,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"鄭捷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"146ca369caaa2ecb175703b9f38871c16ad02c11","tid":939743,"uid":82640,"like":687,"dislike":16,"score":671,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"要幾咁毒同失敗先嬲到要隨機殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe404983900e2c94a3de74899bfb3edf6db64978","tid":939743,"uid":26015,"like":418,"dislike":3,"score":415,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"目的是對社會跟女性復仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比女飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"